  "Hydrostatic pressure at depth h below the surface is P = w*h, where w is the weight density of the fluid (force per unit volume). For water, w = 62.4 lb/ft^3 or 9800 N/m^3.": "地表下深度 h 的氢静压为 P = w *h, 其重量密度为液体(单位体积的强度),对水, w = 62.4 lb/ft3 或 9800 N/m3。",
  "The hydrostatic force on a submerged horizontal plate of area A at depth h in water (weight density 62.4 lb/ft^3) is:": "在水深h处(重量密度为62.4磅/ft}3),A区水下水平板上的静水力为:",
