  "62.4 * h": "62.4 * h",
  "62.4 * h^2 * A": "62.4 * h2 * A",
  "For a horizontal plate, the pressure is constant across the surface: P = 62.4*h. The force is F = P * A = 62.4*h*A. Integration is not needed because the depth is the same everywhere on a horizontal plate.": "横向板块的表面压力不变:P=62.4*h。 压力是F=P * A=62.4*h*A。 不需要整合,因为横向板块的深度是相同的。",
  "Why is integration needed to find hydrostatic force on a vertical plate?": "为什么需要在垂直板块上找到静水力的一体化?",
  "Because the plate is curved": "因为盘子是弯曲的",
  "Because the fluid is moving": "因为流体在移动",
  "Because the plate has a non-uniform thickness": "因为板的厚度不统一",
  "Because the pressure varies with depth across the plate": "因为压力随板盘的深度而变化",
  "On a vertical plate, different horizontal strips are at different depths, so each strip experiences a different pressure. Integration sums the forces on all these infinitesimally thin horizontal strips to find the total hydrostatic force.": "在垂直板块上,不同的横向条纹在不同的深度上,因此每个条纹都经历了不同的压力。 集成将所有这些微薄的横向条纹的力量加在一起,以找到总静水力。",
  "A rectangular plate 4 ft wide is submerged vertically in water with its top edge at depth 2 ft and bottom edge at depth 6 ft. The hydrostatic force is (w = 62.4 lb/ft^3):": "矩形板4英尺宽,垂直淹没在水中,其顶部边缘在深2英尺处,底部边缘在深6英尺处。",
  "62.4 * integral from 0 to 4 of h^2 dh": "62.4 * 等于2 dh时0到4的有机体",
  "62.4 * 4 * 4": "62.4 * 4 * 4 4",
  "62.4 * integral from 2 to 6 of 4h dh": "62.4 * 4h dh 2至6的有机体",
  "62.4 * 4 * 6": "62.4 * 4 * 6",
  "At depth h, the pressure is 62.4*h and the width is 4 ft. The force on a strip at depth h is 62.4*h*4*dh. Total force = 62.4 * integral from 2 to 6 of 4h dh = 249.6 * [h^2/2] from 2 to 6 = 249.6(18 - 2) = 249.6(16) = 3993.6 lb.": "h深度时,压力为62.4*h,宽度为4英尺。深度时,带状力为62.4*h*4*dh。总力=62.4*,从4 dh=249.6的2至6 等于249.6 *[h2/2],从2至6=249.6(18-2)=249.6(16)=3993.6磅b。",
  "What is the hydrostatic force on a rectangular plate 3 ft wide submerged vertically with its top edge at the water surface and its bottom edge at 5 ft depth?": "长方形板3英尺宽的垂直淹没,顶部边缘位于水面,底部边缘位于5英尺深的矩形板块3英尺宽的静水力是什么?",
  "4680 lb": "4680磅",
