  "F = 62.4 * integral from 0 to 5 of 3h dh = 62.4 * 3 * [h^2/2] from 0 to 5 = 187.2 * 12.5 = 2340 lb.": "F = 62.4 * 3 dh 3 dh 0 5 = 62.4 * 3 * 0 = 5 = 187.2 * 12.5 = 2340 lb。",
  "A triangular plate with base 6 ft at the top and vertex pointing down is submerged so its top edge is at the surface. If the plate extends 4 ft down, the width at depth h is:": "底部6英尺的三角板,顶部和顶部向下倾斜的三角板被淹没,其顶边缘在表面。如果板面向下延伸4英尺,深处的宽度为:",
  "6h": "6小时",
