  "6 - h": "6 - 小时",
  "6h/4": "6h/4,6h/4",
  "The triangle has base 6 ft at h = 0 (the top) and vertex at h = 4 (the bottom). By similar triangles, at depth h the width = 6(1 - h/4) = 6(4 - h)/4. At h = 0, width = 6; at h = 4, width = 0.": "三角形以 h = 0 (顶部) 和 h = 4 = 4 (底部) 为基数 6 平方英尺, 顶部) 和顶部为 h = 4 (底部) 。 类似三角形, 深处宽度 h = 6(1 - h/4) = 6 (4 - h)/4 。 h = 0, 宽度 = 6; h = 4 宽 = 0 。",
  "The force on a semicircular plate of radius 3 ft submerged vertically with its diameter at the surface (curved part below) in water is set up as:": "半径3英尺垂直淹没,直径在水中表面(以下弯曲部分)的半圆形板块上,其威力设置如下:",
  "62.4 * integral from 0 to 3 of 2*sqrt(9 - h^2) * h dh": "62.4 * 2*sqrt(9 - h2) * h dh 中0至3的有机体",
  "62.4 * integral from 0 to 3 of 3h dh": "62.4 * 3h 3 dh0至3的有机体",
  "62.4 * integral from -3 to 3 of sqrt(9 - x^2) dx": "62.4 * 3至3平方米(9 - x%2) dx",
  "62.4 * integral from 0 to 3 of pi*h dh": "62.4 * bixin 零至3 pi*h dh 元件",
  "For a semicircle of radius 3 with diameter at the surface, at depth h the horizontal width is 2*sqrt(9 - h^2) (from the circle equation x^2 + h^2 = 9). The force on a strip at depth h is 62.4 * h * 2*sqrt(9 - h^2) dh.": "对于在表面直径的半圆半径3半圆3,在深处h,水平宽度为2*sqrt(9 - h2)(圆形方程式 x2 + h2 = 9),深度h的条状力为62.4 * h * 2 *sqrt(9 - h2) dh。",
  "If fluid density doubles, the hydrostatic force on a submerged plate:": "如果液体密度翻倍,水下板块上的静水力:",
  "Quadruples": "四团数",
  "Doubles": "双双",
  "Stays the same": "保持原样",
  "Halves": "减半",
  "Hydrostatic force is directly proportional to the weight density of the fluid: F = w * integral of h * L(h) dh. If w doubles, F doubles. The geometry of the plate and the depth distribution are unchanged.": "F = w * h * L(h) dh. 如果w 加倍, F 加倍。 板块的几何和深度分布没有变化。",
  "A square plate (side 2 m) is submerged vertically in oil (density 800 kg/m^3, g = 9.8 m/s^2) with its top edge at 1 m depth. The hydrostatic force is:": "一个平方板(2米边)垂直淹没在石油中(密度800公斤/立方米3,g=9.8米/平方米2),其顶端深1米。",
  "9800 * integral from 0 to 2 of 2h dh": "9800 * 2 h 2 dh 的0到 2 英寸的有机体",
  "800 * integral from 1 to 3 of 2h dh": "800 * 2h dh 的1至3的有机体",
  "9800 * 0.8 * 2 * 4": "9800 * 0800 * 0.8 * 2 * 4",
  "9800 * 0.8 * integral from 1 to 3 of 2h dh": "9800 * 0800 * 0.8 * 2h dh 的1至3的有机体",
  "The weight density of the oil is rho*g = 800*9.8 = 7840 = 9800*0.8 N/m^3. The plate runs from depth h = 1 to h = 3 (top at 1 m, side length 2 m). Width is constant at 2 m. F = 7840 * integral from 1 to 3 of 2h dh.": "油的重量密度为 rho*g = 800*9.8 = 7840 = 9800*0.8 N/m3. 油板的深度 h = 1 = 3 (顶部1米,侧长2米)。",
  "Pascal's principle states that pressure applied to a confined fluid:": "Pascal的原则规定,对封闭液体施加的压力:",
  "Is transmitted equally in all directions throughout the fluid": "贯穿流体,在流体各处,传播相等。",
  "Is proportional to the volume of the fluid": "与液体体积成比例",
  "Only acts downward": "仅向下",
  "Decreases with depth": "深度减少",
  "Pascal's principle states that a change in pressure applied to an enclosed fluid is transmitted undiminished to every portion of the fluid and the walls of the container. This is the basis for hydraulic systems.": "Pascal原则规定,对封闭液体施压的改变,对容器每一部分液体和墙壁的传承不受减损,这是液压系统的基础。",
  "What is 'hydrostatic pressure'?": "什么是“静水压力”?",
  "The force of a fluid on a moving object": "流体在移动对象上的强度",
  "Pressure caused by moving water": "移动水造成的压力",
  "Pressure exerted by a fluid at rest due to the weight of fluid above a given point": "由于某一点以上的液体重量,由液体在休息时施加的压力",
  "The atmospheric pressure at sea level": "海平面大气压力",
  "Hydrostatic pressure is the pressure exerted by a fluid at rest due to gravity. At a depth h below the surface, the hydrostatic pressure is P = rho*g*h (or P = w*h where w is weight density). It increases linearly with depth.": "静态压力是指液体在休息时因重力而施加的压力。在地表下深处,静态压力为P = rho*g*h(或P = wh,其中重量密度为湿重)。它随着深度线性增加。",
  "What does 'hydrostatic force' mean?": "\"静水力\"是什么意思?",
  "The force of flowing water on a dam": "在大坝上流水的力量",
  "The buoyant force on a floating object": "漂浮物体的浮力",
  "The total force exerted by a static fluid on a surface due to pressure": "压力下静态液体在表面施加的总力",
  "The force needed to pump water": "抽水所需的水力",
  "Hydrostatic force is the total force that a fluid at rest exerts on a surface. It is found by integrating the pressure (which varies with depth) over the area of the surface: F = integral of P * dA.": "静水力是休息时液体在表面施压的总力,通过将表面区域的压力(因深度不同而不同)集成发现:F = P * dA的有机体。",
  "What does 'weight density' mean?": "\"重量密度\"是什么意思?",
  "Force per unit area": "部队每个单位地区",
  "Mass per unit area": "单位单位面积质量",
  "Mass per unit volume": "每单位质量量",
  "Weight (gravitational force) per unit volume": "单位体积重量(重力)",
  "Weight density (w) is the weight per unit volume of a substance. It equals mass density (rho) times gravitational acceleration (g): w = rho*g. For water, w is approximately 62.4 lb/ft^3 or 9800 N/m^3.": "重量密度(w)是物质单位体积的重量。当质量密度(rho)乘以重力加速度(g): w = rho*g。对于水, W约为62.4 lb/ft3或9800 N/m3。",
  "What does 'fluid statics' mean?": "流体静态是什么意思?",
  "The study of fluids in motion": "研究流动中的液体,",
  "The study of fluid evaporation": "研究液体蒸发",
  "The study of electrical charges in fluids": "研究液体中的电荷",
  "The study of fluids at rest and the forces they exert": "研究休息时的液体和它们施加的力",
  "Fluid statics (or hydrostatics) is the branch of physics that studies fluids at rest. It deals with the conditions under which fluids are in equilibrium and the forces they exert on surfaces. Key concepts include hydrostatic pressure and buoyancy.": "流体静态(或水文静态)是研究休息时的液体的物理分支,涉及液体处于平衡状态的条件及其在表面所施加的力量,关键概念包括静水压力和浮力。",
  "What is 'pressure' in physics?": "物理学中的“压力”是什么?",
  "Force per unit volume": "部队每单位数量",
  "Energy per unit area": "单位单位面积能源面积",
  "Pressure is defined as force per unit area: P = F/A. Its SI unit is the pascal (Pa), where 1 Pa = 1 N/m^2. In fluid mechanics, pressure at a point acts equally in all directions.": "P=F/A。 其SI单元是帕斯卡尔(Pa),其中1帕=1 N/m2. 在液压力力学中,一个点的压力在所有方向都平等。",
  "What is the 'centroid' of a submerged plate and why is it relevant to fluid force?": "水下板块的“中心机器人”是什么? 为什么它与液态力有关?",
  "The point of zero pressure on the plate": "板盘的零压点",
  "The deepest point on the plate; force is maximum there": "板盘的最深点; 最大力",
  "The center of buoyancy of the plate": "板盘浮力中心",
  "The geometric center of the plate; the force equals pressure at the centroid times the area": "板块的几何中心; 压力等于在中间体的压力乘以面积",
  "The centroid is the geometric center of the plate. For a flat plate submerged in a fluid, the total hydrostatic force equals the pressure at the centroid multiplied by the plate's area: F = (w * h_centroid) * A. This is a useful shortcut for uniform-density fluids.": "中央机器人是板块的几何中心。 对于一个被液体淹没的平板板, 整体静水力等于小行星的压力乘板块面积: F = (w * h_centroid) * A。 对于制服密度液来说, 这是一条有用的捷径。",
  "What does 'gauge pressure' mean?": "\"压力\"是什么意思?",
  "The total pressure including atmospheric pressure": "包括大气压力在内的总压力",
  "The minimum pressure in a fluid": "液体中最小的压强",
  "The pressure above atmospheric pressure, equal to the hydrostatic pressure alone": "高于大气压力的压力,等于仅静水压力",
  "Pressure measured using a gauge device": "使用测量仪表设备测量压力",
  "Gauge pressure is the pressure relative to atmospheric pressure. It equals the absolute pressure minus atmospheric pressure. In hydrostatic problems, P_gauge = rho*g*h, which is just the pressure due to the fluid column above the point.": "Gauge 压力是相对于大气压力的压力。 它等于绝对压力减去大气压力。 在静水问题中, P_gauge = rho*g*h, 这只是点上方液柱的压力。",
  "What does 'Archimedes' principle' state?": "什么是“Arnimedes”原则的状态?",
  "An object in a fluid experiences an upward buoyant force equal to the weight of the fluid it displaces": "流体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体 体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体 体体体体体体体体体体体,体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体 体体体体体体体体体体体体体,体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体体力的体力",
  "Pressure at a given depth is equal in all directions": "在给定深度处的压力在所有方向均相等",
  "Fluid flows from high pressure to low pressure": "从高压流流到低压",
  "Heavier objects always sink": "较重物体总是沉没",
  "Archimedes' principle states that a body wholly or partially submerged in a fluid experiences an upward buoyant force equal to the weight of the fluid displaced. This principle can be derived using integration of hydrostatic pressure over the body's surface.": "Archimedes原则指出,在流体中全部或部分沉没的体体经历着相当于流体流体脱落重量的向上浮力,可以通过对体表表面的静水压力进行集成来得出这一原则。",
  "What is a 'pascal' as a unit of pressure?": "什么是“帕斯卡”作为压力单位?",
  "1 newton per square meter": "每平方米1牛顿",
  "1 joule per cubic meter": "每立方米1焦耳",
  "1 newton per cubic meter": "每立方米1牛顿",
  "1 kilogram per square meter": "每平方米1千克",
  "A pascal (Pa) is the SI unit of pressure, defined as one newton per square meter (1 Pa = 1 N/m^2). Standard atmospheric pressure is approximately 101,325 Pa.": "Pascal(Pa)是SI压力单位,定义为每平方米1牛顿(1帕=1牛顿/平方米)。 标准大气压力约为101 325帕。",
  "What does it mean for pressure to be 'isotropic' in a fluid at rest?": "休息时在液体里 压力是\"异种\"是什么意思?",
  "Pressure is zero at the surface": "表面压力为零",
  "Pressure varies depending on the shape of the container": "压力因容器形状不同而不同",
  "Pressure only acts downward": "压力仅向下",
  "At any given point in the fluid, the pressure is the same in all directions": "在液体中的任何某一点, 压力在所有方向都是相同的",
  "Isotropic pressure means that at any point in a fluid at rest, the pressure has the same value in every direction. A fluid pushes equally in all directions at a given depth. This is a fundamental property of fluids in static equilibrium.": "粒度压力意味着在休息时的液体中, 压力在每一个方向都有相同的价值。 液体在给定深度的所有方向上都同样地推进。 这是静态平衡中液体的基本属性 。",
  "A rectangular swimming pool is 10 m long, 4 m wide, and 3 m deep. What is the hydrostatic force on one of the 10 m by 3 m walls? (Use water weight density = 9800 N/m^3.)": "矩形游泳池长10米,宽4米,深3米。 10米中1米长3米长的墙壁的静水力是什么? (使用水的重量密度=9800牛顿/立方米。 )",
  "294,000 N": "294 000努",
  "441,000 N": "441 000奈",
  "147,000 N": "147,000 N",
  "882,000 N": "882 000奈",
  "F = 9800 * integral from 0 to 3 of 10*h dh = 98,000 * [h^2/2] from 0 to 3 = 98,000 * 4.5 = 441,000 N.": "F = 9800 * 10 dh = 98,000 * 零 = 9800 * 3 等于0 = 3 = 9800 * 等于 98,000 * 等于 0 = 3 = 98,000 * = 4.5 = 441,000 N。",
  "A dam has a trapezoidal face: 100 m wide at the top (water surface), 60 m wide at the bottom, and 20 m deep. What integral gives the hydrostatic force on the dam face? (w = 9800 N/m^3)": "水坝的顶部(水面)宽度为100米,底部宽度为60米,深度为20米。 大坝的静水力是由什么构成的? (w = 9800 N/m3)",
  "9800 * integral from 0 to 20 of 100*h dh": "9800 * 从100* h dh零度到20公分之0至20的有机体",
  "9800 * integral from 0 to 20 of (60 + 2h) * h dh": "9800 *0至20(60+2h) * h dh)",
  "9800 * integral from 0 to 20 of (100 - 2h) * h dh": "9800 * 零至20(100-2h) * h dh)",
  "9800 * integral from 0 to 20 of 60*h dh": "9800 * 60* h dh的0至20之间",
  "At depth h, the width of the trapezoid decreases linearly from 100 (at h=0) to 60 (at h=20). Width = 100 - (100-60)/20 * h = 100 - 2h. The force integral is 9800 * integral from 0 to 20 of (100 - 2h)*h dh.": "在深度 h 时, 的宽度从100( h=0) 线性下降至60( h=20) 。 宽度 = 100 - ( 100- 60/20) * h = 100 - 2h 。 积分为 9800 * 零 - 20 ( 100 - 2h) * dh) 。",
  "An aquarium has a circular viewing window of radius 1 m, with its center at a depth of 3 m below the water surface. The total hydrostatic force on the window is:": "水族馆有一个半径1米的圆形观察窗口,其中心在水面下3米深处。",
  "9800 * 3 * 2*pi*1 N": "9800 * 3 * 2 *pi *1 N",
  "9800 * 3 * pi * 1^2 N": "9800 * 3 * pi * 1__2 N",
  "9800 * pi * 1^2 N": "9800 * pi * 1__2 N",
  "9800 * 4 * pi * 1^2 N": "9800 * 4 * pi * 1×2 N",
  "For a flat plate, F = (pressure at centroid) * area = (9800 * 3) * (pi * 1^2) = 29,400*pi N. The centroid of the circle is at its center, which is at depth 3 m.": "对于平板板,F = (中子压力) * 区域= (9800 * 3) * (pi * 12) = 29,400 *pi N. 圆圆的中间体位于其中心,深度为3米。",
  "A triangular gate in a dam has its vertex at the water surface and base of 8 ft at a depth of 6 ft. What is the hydrostatic force on the gate? (w = 62.4 lb/ft^3)": "水坝中的三角门在水面和深6英尺的8英尺底部有其顶部。 门上的静水力是什么? (w = 62.4 lb/ft}3)",
  "2995.2 lb": "2995.2磅b",
  "8985.6 lb": "8985.6磅b",
  "5990.4 lb": "5990.4磅b",
  "4492.8 lb": "4492.8磅b",
  "The width at depth h is (8/6)*h = 4h/3 (by similar triangles, 0 at vertex/surface, 8 at depth 6). F = 62.4 * integral from 0 to 6 of h*(4h/3) dh = 62.4*(4/3) * integral from 0 to 6 of h^2 dh = 83.2 * [h^3/3] from 0 to 6 = 83.2 * 72 = 5990.4 lb.": "深度 h 的宽度为 8/6 * h = 4h/3 (以类似三角形计算,在顶部/表面为0,在深度为8 6) F = 62.4 * h* (4h/3) dh = 62.4* (4/3) * 从 0 = 6 = 83.2 * [h3/3] 从 0 到 6 = 83.2 * 72 = 5990.4 lb 中,从 0 = 6 = 62.4 dh = 62.4* (4/3) * 从 0 到 6 = 83.2 * [h3/3] 从 0 到 6 = 83.2 * 72 = 5990.4 lb 。",
  "A vertical plate in the shape of a semicircle of radius 2 m is submerged in oil (weight density 7840 N/m^3) with its diameter at the surface. What is the hydrostatic force on the plate?": "半径2米半圆形的垂直板块被浸在油(重量密度7840牛顿/立方米)中,其直径在表面。 板块的静水力是什么?",
  "7840 * integral from 0 to 2 of 4h dh N": "7840 * N4 dh 4 dh 零度至2度的有机体",
  "7840 * integral from 0 to 2 of 2h*sqrt(4 - h^2) dh N": "7840 * 2h*sqrt(4 - h2) dh N. 0至2",
  "7840 * integral from 0 to 2 of pi*h dh N": "7840 * 从0到2 pi*h dh N",
  "7840 * 2 * pi N": "7840 * 2 * pi N",
  "At depth h, the width of the semicircle is 2*sqrt(r^2 - h^2) = 2*sqrt(4 - h^2). The force = 7840 * integral from 0 to 2 of h * 2*sqrt(4 - h^2) dh. Using substitution u = 4 - h^2, this integral evaluates to 7840*(2/3)(4)^(3/2) = 7840*16/3.": "在深度 h ,半圆圆的宽度为 2 *sqrt(r2 - h2) = 2 *sqrt(4 - h2) = 2 *sqrt(4 - h2) 。 力 = 7840 * 2 h * 2 *sqrt(4 - h2) 2 dh. 使用替代 u = 4 - h2, 这个整体值为 7840* (2/3)(4)(3/2) = 7840 *16/3。",
  "A submarine's circular porthole has a diameter of 0.5 m and its center is 200 m below the ocean surface. If seawater has weight density 10,050 N/m^3, what is the hydrostatic force on the porthole?": "潜艇圆孔的直径为0.5米,中心在海洋表面下方200米,如果海水的重量密度为10 050牛顿/立方米,则港口口的静水力是什么?",
  "Approximately 197,300 N": "约197 300 N",
  "Approximately 789,200 N": "约789 200 N",
  "Approximately 98,650 N": "约98 650奈",
  "Approximately 394,600 N": "约394 600 N",
  "F = pressure at centroid * area = (10,050 * 200) * (pi * 0.25^2) = 2,010,000 * pi * 0.0625 = 2,010,000 * 0.19635 = 394,600 N (approximately). The centroid is at the center of the circle, 200 m deep.": "F = 中心机器人* 区域的压力= (10 050 * 200) * (pi * 0.252) = 2 010 000 * pi * 0.0625 = 2 010 000 * 0.19635 = 394 600 N(约合). 环形中心为200米深200米。",
  "A water trough has a semicircular cross-section with radius 1 ft. When filled to the top, what is the hydrostatic force on one flat end? (w = 62.4 lb/ft^3)": "水槽中有一个半圆形横截面,半径为1英尺。 填充到顶部时,一个平端的静水力是什么? (w = 62.4 lb/ft}3)",
  "83.2 lb": "83.2磅",
