  "41.6 lb": "41.6磅b",
  "With diameter at the top (surface), at depth h, the width is 2*sqrt(1 - h^2). F = 62.4 * integral from 0 to 1 of h * 2*sqrt(1 - h^2) dh. Let u = 1 - h^2, du = -2h dh. F = 62.4 * integral from 1 to 0 of -sqrt(u) du = 62.4 * [2u^(3/2)/3] from 0 to 1 = 62.4 * 2/3 = 41.6 lb.": "直径在顶部(地表)深h处,宽度为2*sqrt(1 - h2),F=62.4*0至1 h *2*sqrt(1 - h2) dh. Let u = 1 - h2, du = - 2h dh. F = 62.4 * 1至0 - Sqrt(u) du = 62.4 * [2u(3/2)/3] 0至1= 62.4 * 2/3 = 41.6 lb.",
  "A tank shaped like an inverted triangle (vertex at bottom) is 6 m wide at the top and 4 m deep. It is filled with a chemical solution of weight density 12,000 N/m^3. What is the force on one triangular end?": "形状像反向三角形的罐体( 底部的顶端的顶端的顶端外形) 6米宽, 4米深。 它装满了一个重量密度密度为12,000 N/ 立方米的化学溶液。 一个三角形端的强度是多少 ?",
  "128,000 N": "128 000奈",
  "64,000 N": "64,000奈",
  "192,000 N": "192 000 N",
  "96,000 N": "96,000奈",
  "At depth h from the surface, the width = 6(1 - h/4) = 6(4-h)/4 = 3(4-h)/2. F = 12,000 * integral from 0 to 4 of h * 3(4-h)/2 dh = 18,000 * integral from 0 to 4 of (4h - h^2) dh = 18,000 * [2h^2 - h^3/3] from 0 to 4 = 18,000 * (32 - 64/3) = 18,000 * (96/3 - 64/3) = 18,000 * 32/3 = 192,000 N. Let me recheck: 18000*(32/3) = 192,000. Hmm -- checking the width function: top is h=0, width=6. Bottom is h=4, width=0. So width = 6*(4-h)/4 = 3(4-h)/2. F = 12000 * integral of h*(3(4-h)/2) dh = 12000*(3/2)*integral of (4h-h^2)dh from 0 to 4 = 18000*[2h^2 - h^3/3] from 0 to 4 = 18000*(32-64/3) = 18000*(32/3) = 192,000 N. So the answer is 192,000 N. But that matches option C. Let me verify: F = 12000*integral from 0 to 4 of h * (3(4-h)/2) dh. The coefficient is 12000*3/2 = 18000. Integral of (4h-h^2) from 0 to 4 = [2h^2-h^3/3] from 0 to 4 = 32-64/3 = (96-64)/3 = 32/3. So F = 18000*(32/3) = 192,000 N. The correct answer should be 192,000.": "在地表深度h处,宽度=6(1 - h/4)=6(4-h)/4=6(4-h)/4=3(3、4-h)/2/2。F=12 000 * 整件从0到4 h * 3(4-4)/2 dh=18 000 * 整件从0到4 (4-h)2 dh=18 000 * [2h2/2 - h3/3] dh=10.8 * (32 - 64/3) =18,000 * (32 - 64/3) = 0(4/3-h)/4 = 0/3 = 312 000 N. 3/3 = 3 3 3 = 3 312 000 N。让我重新检查宽度函数:顶是 h=0, h=0,宽度=6. 底是 h=4,宽度=4 4;宽度= 6* (4-h)= 3 18* (4-h) 2. Fxx 193(3xxxxx 192xxxx).",
  "An oil storage tank has a rectangular inspection hatch 0.5 m wide and 0.8 m tall on its side. The top of the hatch is 2 m below the oil surface (oil weight density = 8500 N/m^3). What is the force on the hatch?": "储油罐的侧面有长方形检查舱口0.5米宽,0.8米高,舱口顶部在油面下2米以下(油重密度=8500牛顿/立方米)。",
  "4,080 N": "4 080 N 4 080 N",
