  "8,160 N": "8,8,160 N",
  "10,200 N": "10 200 N 10 200 N",
  "F = 8500 * integral from 2 to 2.8 of 0.5*h dh = 4250 * [h^2/2] from 2 to 2.8 = 4250 * (3.92 - 2) = 4250 * 1.92 = 8,160 N. Alternatively, F = pressure at centroid * area = 8500 * 2.4 * (0.5 * 0.8) = 8500 * 2.4 * 0.4 = 8,160 N.": "F=8500 * 从2等于0.5*h dh = 4250 * [h2/2]从2等于 2.8= 4250 * (3.92-2)= 4250 * 1.92= 8 160 N. 或者,F= 中子机组的压力= 8500 * 2.4 * (0.5 * 0.8) = 8500 * 2.4 * 2.4 * 2.4 * 0.4 = 8 160 N.",
  "A flood barrier must withstand hydrostatic force from water 5 m deep. The barrier is 20 m wide. If the safety specification requires it to hold 3 times the calculated hydrostatic force, what force must the barrier be designed to withstand? (w = 9800 N/m^3)": "防洪屏障必须能够承受来自5米深水的静水力。 屏障宽20米。 如果安全规范要求它保持所计算的静水力的3倍,那么必须设计何种阻力来承受? (w = 9800 N/m3)",
